  "meta": {
    "title": "the midway at night",
    "composer": "Am\u00e9lie Rocha (hummed to the staff composer, 1990)",
    "for": "Fey Faire \u00b7 midway / negotiation / fortune scenes",
    "notes": "A slow 3/4 carousel waltz in D minor. The hand-crank music-box tune the player hears at the carousel and cannot place. soft_sine carries the box melody, pad turns underneath like the platform itself, bass marks the downbeat the way a carousel pole passes the operator. 24 bars at 90."
